title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.7 - Responsibility for prompt determination of eligibility
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.7 - Responsibility for prompt determination of eligibility

State Regulations

The decision to accept or deny the application shall be made as soon as sufficient information to make a determination about eligibility is obtained. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
43-2.7

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
